{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_01","textHome":"我是百江渚的说！要自我介绍吗？@那么，就只要记住一件事就行了……@小渚最喜欢的食物就是奶酪！@是奶酪的说！不管是味道还是形状都最喜欢了！@有圆滚滚的，也有棱角分明的……@光是看着就兴致高涨的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_17","textHome":"虽然我在吹奏部选了小号，@但一开始我完全吹不出声音……@无论怎么吹都只有「嘶～」一个音……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_18","textHome":"有一天，我发现了！@用吃奶酪时的口型，小号就能吹出声音！@这是真的！@看！就是这种感觉的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_19","textHome":"嗯嗯……看来小渚的魔力又提高了的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_20","textHome":"好清爽的感觉……@还有我的肚子饿了的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_21","textHome":"我真正喜欢上奶酪，@是妈妈给我做奶酪蛋糕的时候。@那真是好美味的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_22","textHome":"妈妈只给我做过一次奶酪蛋糕。@之后就生病住院了，住院了也就做不了了，@而现在她已经不在人世了的说。@所以，那块奶酪蛋糕，@我再也没能吃上第二次的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_23","textHome":"爸爸在妈妈生病之后不久就失踪了的说。@不过……我记得在我吃妈妈做的奶酪蛋糕时，@爸爸妈妈都在我的眼前笑着的场景……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_24","textHome":"啊，你来了的说！@我等你等得肚子都饿了……@那么，走吧！去吃奶酪的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_25","textHome":"呜喵……啊啊呜喵……我开动了……@嗯？……刚刚的是……梦？@啊！差一点点就能吃上极品奶酪了！@我要再回去睡一觉的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_26","textHome":"小渚最喜欢的午饭是意大利面！@然后撒上奶酪粉！@可以说不撒奶酪粉的意大利面@根本算不上意大利面的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_02","textHome":"啊呜……嗯……这个真是……@嗯？啊、啊啊！@呃……我叫百江渚的说！@诶，你问我在吃什么吗？@嗯哼哼……当然是奶酪的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_27","textHome":"傍晚听到学校吹奏部传来的练习声时，@心里就会咯噔一下的说……@有些悲伤，或是有些怀念……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_28","textHome":"渚是小孩子，所以不会熬夜！@所以我已经睡觉了！@也就是说刚刚这些都是梦话！@ZZZ……的说……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_29","textHome":"工作或是学习累了的时候，没有精神的时候，@伤心的时候……只要有……@对……奶——啊啊，等等！听我说完嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_30","textHome":"对手是魔女。@但它的成因，却是散布诅咒时的自己……@真是的！为什么会变成这样啊！？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_31","textHome":"无尽镜界……这是镜子做成的通道……@是神滨市才有的特殊现象……@我要记笔记的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_32","textHome":"大家，来吃点心吧！@每一种都是奶酪味的，很好吃的说！@然后就拿出干劲努力吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_33","textHome":"诶？渚喜欢的奶酪蛋糕？@那当然是……重乳酪蛋糕的说！@软软的，湿润的感觉……我最喜欢的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":200}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_34","textHome":"又好吃名字又可爱的奶酪@就是「佩科里诺」的说！@怎么说好呢……嗯……佩科里诺！@光是这样感觉就能开心起来！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_35","textHome":"对小渚来说，最棒的治愈就是，@拉可雷特干酪在嘴里融化的的那一瞬间！@可以一直这么回味下去的说！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":1}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200700,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2007_00_36","textHome":"「渚」，有海岸边的意思。@妈妈曾经对我说……@有一天她会带我去海边……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_033.exp.json","id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200700,"motion":300}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"f